	$ go test -race

	==================
	WARNING: DATA RACE
	Read by goroutine 8:
	  racy_server.go:13 +0x30

	Previous write by goroutine 7:
	  racy_server.go:13 +0x4c

	Goroutine 8 (running) created at:
	  racy_handler_test.go:12 +0x86
	  testing.tRunner()
